nderstand a proverb, and the interpretation; the words of the wise, and their dark sayings.","year":-1000},{"id":"recHOAL5d7C0zct2Z","ref":"Prov.1.7","text":"The fear of the LORD is the beginning of knowledge: but fools despise wisdom and instruction.","year":-1000},{"id":"reclisOgseRlnMcVU","ref":"Prov.1.8","text":"My son, hear the instruction of thy father, and forsake not the law of thy mother:","year":-1000}]}
